---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Best Monitor Light Bar for Eye Care 2026';
const pageDescription = 'Honest review of screen light bars. Eliminate desk glare and reduce eye strain during late-night work sessions.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} articleSchema={{headline: pageTitle, description: pageDescription, datePublished: '2026-05', authorName: 'Toolwise Team'}} />
    <style>
      main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; }
      h1 { color: #232f3e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .product-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
      .product-box h2 { margin-top: 0; }
      .product-box ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #ff9900; color: #000; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
      .btn:hover { background: #e68a00; }
      .disclaimer { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 1rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Best Monitor Light Bar for Eye Care</h1>
      <div class="meta">Updated May 2026 · Under $40</div>

      <p>Desk lamps reflect off your monitor and create glare. A monitor light bar hangs above the screen and shines light downward onto your desk — no reflection, no wasted space, and significantly less eye strain during 10-hour workdays.</p>

      <div class="product-box">
        <h2>🏆 LED Monitor Light Bar with Touch Control</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Asymmetric optical design</strong> — light hits the desk, not the screen</li>
          <li><strong>3 color temperatures</strong> — 2900K warm, 4000K neutral, 6000K cool white</li>
          <li><strong>Stepless dimming</strong> — touch control from 5% to 100% brightness</li>
          <li><strong>USB powered</strong> — plugs into monitor or laptop, no wall adapter</li>
          <li><strong>Universal mount</strong> — clips onto monitors 0.4" to 1.2" thick</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=monitor+light+bar&tag=toolwise20-20" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Check Current Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

      <h3>Why it beats a desk lamp for monitor users</h3>
      <p>Even the best desk lamp bounces light off your screen. A monitor bar uses an asymmetric lens that directs light at a 45-degree angle onto your keyboard and documents, completely avoiding the monitor surface. The result is a evenly lit desk with zero glare — something no traditional lamp can achieve.</p>

      <h3>Who should buy it</h3>
      <p>Anyone who works past sunset, gamers with multi-monitor setups, and professionals who spend 6+ hours at a screen. It pairs perfectly with our recommended laptop stand and portable monitor — stack them together and you have a complete ergonomic workstation for under $150 total.</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        Disclosure: As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. This review is based on independent research and reader feedback.
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>